    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken absolute pride in keeping it in pristine condition, from the spotless interior to the flawless paint job. It drives like a total dream and has been babied since day one. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 997.1 Carrera S is an investment-grade example of Porsche\u2019s analog peak, featuring the 3.8L flat-six M97 engine with documented bore-score inspections and a reinforced IMS solution. The mechanical integrity is superlative, boasting a dry-sump lubrication system and a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle that delivers power through a perfectly indexed limited-slip differential. Equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and four-piston monoblock Brembo calipers, the chassis dynamics remain as sharp as the day it left Stuttgart. This is a concours-ready specimen with zero fluid seepage, offering the tactile steering feedback and linear power delivery that modern turbocharged units simply cannot replicate.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "One owner. Garage kept. Original paint. No mechanical issues. Full service records included. Interior is spotless.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
