    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with absolutely zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of wear, and the original 'new car' scent lingers. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the precise climate control, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships with a full paper trail included. This is a rare opportunity to own a time-capsule example of automotive excellence, perfect for the most discerning enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
